quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,112,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana umanyilisichi ungwete pa yaŵaliji nkutenda ŵanganyao?”"
  26,113,"“Nganichiŵatu chiŵalanjilo chao ikaŵeje kwa Ambuje ŵangu, ingaŵe mwamanyililaga.”"
  26,114,"“Soni nganimba une jwanti ni kwaŵinga ŵakulupilila.”"
  27,85,"Ni lichisimichika liloŵe (lyachonasiko) pa ŵanganyao ligongo lya lupuso lwao, mwanti ngasakombola kuŵecheta (kwakuliŵalanga)."
  27,86,"Ana nganayiona ŵanganyao yanti Uwwe twatendele chilo kuti apumulejemo, muusi nikuŵa ŵakuloleka? Chisimu mu yalakweyo muŵele mwana ilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵaakukulupilila."
  27,87,"Soni (kumbuchilani) lisiku lyachiligombedwa lipenga nikogopa (kwakuwanako) yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka, ikaŵeje yataachiisaka Allah (kuti ikajogopa), soni yosope ichim’bichilila Jwalakwe ili yakulinandiya."
  28,58,"Soni jilingwajilingwa mwa misi jatwajijonasile, janakutwanjilaga ndamo jao (jambone)! Sanotu amo nimmalo mwao mwanganimutamidweje panyuma pao ikaŵeje panandipe, soni Uwwe niŵatwaliji Ŵawinjila."
  28,59,"Ni nganaŵa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ŵanti nikonanga misi mpaka akatumisye mu nsinda wakwe wekulungwa ntenga jwakwasoomela ŵanganyao ma Ȃya Getu (nkugakanamo nikwajonangaga), soni nganituŵa ŵakujijonanga misi ikaŵeje achimisyeneo ali ŵalupuso."
  28,60,"Soni ichindu iliyose yampedwile iŵele yakusengwasya umi wa duniya ni ipeto yakwe, nambo yaili kwa Allah niyambone nnope soni yakwendelechela, ana ngankuitaga mulunda?"
  29,25,"Sano (Ibrahima) jwatite: “Chisimu jenumanja n’ditendele isanamu (kuŵa yakuigalagatila) kunneka Allah. Chinonyelo chilikati chenu chiŵele cha umi wa pa duniya peuno, nambo lisiku lya Kiyama tinchikanana jwine ni n’jakwe, nambo soni tinchilwesana jwine ni n’jakwe, soni mauto genu ni ku Moto, soni ngasinkola akunkulupusya.”"
  29,26,"Basi Lutwi ŵankulupilile jwalakwe. (Ibrahima) ni jwatite: “Chisimu une ngusama wa kwa Ambuje ŵangu (Allah). Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka.”"
  29,27,"Ni twampele jwalakwe Isihaka ni Yaakubu, ni twaŵisile mu ŵanache ŵakwe utume ni chitabu, ni twampele malipilo gakwe pa duniya, soni chisimu jwalakwe ku Akhera tachiŵa mu ŵandu ŵambone."
  30,4,"Mu yaka igala (yapachilikati cha itatu ni nsano nancheche), chilamusi ni cha Allah paujo ni panyuma (pakupundako), soni lyele lisikulyo (lyatachipunda Aroma kwapunda Afaarisi) ŵakulupilila (Asilamu) tachisengwa."
  30,5,"Ni chikamuchisyo cha Allah. Akunkamuchisyaga jwaakunsaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwachanasa channope."
  30,6,"(Achi ni) chilanga cha Allah. Allah jwangakasa chilanga Chakwe, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ngakumanyilila."